data.description: Great semi-attached brick duplex on Yakona Rd in Towson.  Freshly Painted and well maintained 3BR 2 BA 930 sq foot home with finished basement and incredible fully fenced backyard.  Kitchen features gas cooking with all stainless appliances, small pantry and granite countertops.  Eat-in kitchen with room for a small table.  Second floor has a large primary bedroom and a second smaller bedroom currently used as a home office both with nice looking hardwood floors.  2nd floor bathroom has a single vanity, exhaust fan and tub shower combo.   First floor has a nice size family/living room with ceiling fan and hardwood floors.  Mostly finished carpeted and tiled basement can be third bedroom or office.  Stylish full bathroom on lower level has a tiled tub and shower combo and single vanity.  Laundry in rear of basement with washer and dryer included and access to back yard.  Water Heater replaced less than 2 years ago.  The real gem of this house is the 150ft long fully vinyl fenced rear yard with patio area and lush green grass.  Some patio chairs convey.  The rear fence has built in solar powered lights. Gas powered furnace has recently been serviced. Two space driveway included with the property.  Call now to schedule your appointment. Contact listing agent or alt agent on voicemail for any questions.  Professional photos to follow.
